PrecisAppointment of GEOFFREY BURGESS of Vancouver, British Columbia; DAVID CAVAZZI of Richmond, British Columbia, DAVID CLARK of Duncan, British Columbia, DIANE M. DELVES of Abbotsford, British Coumbia, MICHAEL GROVER of Vancouver, British Columbia, TOM JOHNSTONE of Saturna, British Columbia, MICHAEL NAISH of Courtenay, British Columbia, and BRIAN WALLACE, Q.C. of Victoria, British Columbia; ROGER BEAUPRÉ of Calgary, Alberta, ALAN FENTON of St. Albert, Alberta, RENÉ GAGNÉ of Edmonton, Alberta, ANGUS MacKAY of Edmonton, Alberta, and IKE ZACHAROPOULOS of Calgary, Alberta; L.
